    "Further second-order concepts included black-box algorithms, i.e., nonexplainable AI (n = 12/89, 13.5%) 27, 36, 55, 57, 65, 73, 76, 83, 91, 94, 103, 105, limited engagement and dialog capabilities (n = 10/89, 11.2%) 13, 27, 28, 37, 38, 51, 56, 66, 95, 103, and the inability of self-validation and correction (n = 4/89, 4.5%) 61, 73, 74, 107.",
    "Output limitations.",
