    ", (un-)safeness (n = 39/89, 43.8%) 28, 30, 35, 37, 39, 40, [42] [43] [44] 46, 50, 51, [57] [58] [59] [60] 62, 64, 65, 69, 70, 73, 74, 76, [78] [79] [80] 82, 84, 85, 91, 94, 95, [98] [99] [100] 105, 106, 109, bias (n = 6/89, 6.7%) 26, 32, 34, 36, 66, 103, and the dependence of the quality of output on the prompt-/input provided (n = 27/89, 30.3%) [26] [27] [28] 34, 38, 41, 44, 46, 51, 52, 56, [68] [69] [70] [71] [72] 74, 76, 78, 79, [81] [82] [83] 90, 94, 95, 100, 101 or the environment (n = 16/89, 18%) 13, 34, 46, [49] [50] [51] 54, 58, 60, 72, 73, 88, 90, 93, 97, 109.",
